T11:13:01.000Z","msg":"好詳盡 辛苦哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e80aad5846884f7063302688a3e45e411a06b30","tid":1685050,"uid":336769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:16:38.000Z","msg":"短期計劃應該唔難做 行動組加油"},{"pid":"f1f4e50e28fa0e2122bc4c8d0f92d2662cb5d38e","tid":1685050,"uid":173949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x4dBLxo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx4dBLxo.gif&h=41dcdcf7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e3800487f04f2111167d8292c6a6c1b10ee102f","tid":1685050,"uid":336769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:17:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁正 唔係唔推比合適人才睇"},{"pid":"dd8fe6f48fc3f32e3bea20e59cc5d0e03c02c2bd","tid":1685050,"uid":135332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:19:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係諗得過"},{"pid":"23f0a506573e5b668e9144fe8c7159d182d96d84","tid":1685050,"uid":66611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:22:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先利申理科人，可能內容未必完全正確。 唔好tldr <br />\n<br />\n我哋依家嘅黃色經濟圈其實好流，除非黃店係自置物業或者市場有黃供應商選擇，如果唔係就好易比咗錢藍絲紅底業主同供應商賺。<br />\n<br />\n香港有嘅係人材，冇嘅係發揮機會，與其私有化政府咁遙遠嘅事，不如眾籌一間<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(支那用語唔好介意)</span>民族企業，一間真香港人共有嘅離岸公司，一個富可敵國嘅集團。<br />\n<br />\n小學常識都有教香港產業結構側重金融同服務業，但係偏偏金融同服務業就最容易比人揸住春袋，好似國泰、滙豐依啲曾經引以為傲嘅&ldquo;民族企業&rdquo;，好快就跪低咗；誠哥就唔同喇，除咗百佳屈臣氏依啲小巫，仲有地產、港口、外國天然氣、外國電訊依啲大巫，百足咁多爪驚閪你共產黨咩。<br />\n<br />\n每一個國家背後都一定有幾間可以支撐到經濟嘅企業同埋集團，而依啲企業都以實業為主，日本有Toyota、三菱，韓國有Samsung、LG，德國有西門子、BMW、Benz&hellip;&hellip;唔舉太多例子喇，我想表達嘅係實業先可以長遠支撐經濟發展，國民支持自己國家嘅企業，企業提供就業同價廉物美產品比自己國民，形成一個自給自足嘅經濟圈(依一刻我哋最少有二百萬基數)。<br />\n<br />\n依一個富可敵國嘅集團最初應該以真香港人為服務對象，之後逐漸擴張賺埋藍絲同埋其他國家錢，回饋返真香港人。業務應該包括地產(供應房屋、鋪位、土地)，輕工業(供應食品、藥品、日用品)，重工業(煉鋼、軍工)，創科(R&amp;D)，組成一條唔洗靠外人嘅供應鏈，日後可以做埋保險、融資等嘅金融業務，進一步擴展市場。<br />\n<br />\n可能太過理想，不過做得到依步唔止黃色經濟圏，香港獨立都指日可待。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n舊post搬過嚟，推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b69325dff2d0e7d6b4ed3995113fbcd5ac97ad52","tid":1685050,"uid":127952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:25:27.000Z","msg":"高質Post 推"},{"pid":"4672110668135322250e5d3c1c9d2b8b28ba3e7d","tid":1685050,"uid":234271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:29:35.000Z","msg":"創立公司求組隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbdf4cb99b243c3f2e4fe1f7eef03d62b0c3441","tid":1685050,"uid":66246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd8fe6f48fc3f32e3bea20e59cc5d0e03c02c2bd","tid":1685050,"uid":135332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:19:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係諗得過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:30:16.000Z","msg":"組班底未？"},{"pid":"6118a01241cf3e8cdb87e9558756f5fc03f5c51a","tid":1685050,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e3fc37b6782243b7cbbac4c8f0e860d7d0951b","tid":1685050,"uid":234271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1dbdf4cb99b243c3f2e4fe1f7eef03d62b0c3441","tid":1685050,"uid":66246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd8fe6f48fc3f32e3bea20e59cc5d0e03c02c2bd","tid":1685050,"uid":135332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:19:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係諗得過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:30:16.000Z","msg":"組班底未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:31:26