似國難咁日日搵狗黎搞鳩你，沒收晒你所有資產"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T18:06:55.000Z","msg":"第一個你可以放心，可以去BVI 註冊公司<br />\n第二個你都可以放心，香港公司報税係要搵auditor搞，幾千蚊連埋答Q，如果有奇怪arrangements怕出事仲可以拎advance ruling。利申：會計友<br />\n三同四就比較難防，但我地係要建立一個圈子<br />\n，除非佢封哂啲黃店，如果唔係佢搞唔到幾多個"},{"pid":"24dc8278ddd5ca4b9b1dd643050797a60177cfe0","tid":1685050,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T18:08:54.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98263a8cf06de2dae173c97b2bd6bd4708381ff2","tid":1685050,"uid":244451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T18:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2d662cd120b43008ef8cc0edf4558ee4ef75032","tid":1685050,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b94ecbd752352cba079255c894aa9883f77420a7","tid":1685050,"uid":244451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e2e6836f331610073ddd337cca5f5a18321e50f","tid":1685050,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:02:37.000Z","msg":"答我一問題先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你要創造獨立經濟圈，但係服從港共法律<br />\n點樣阻止佢用立法，司法，執法權搞鳩你？<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:58:21.000Z","msg":"如果要搞佢就要全部公司都得返國企中資同藍企<br />\n同埋佢點立法去控制我地去邊間公司度買野？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T19:14:17.000Z","msg":"依家香港本身你唔係支資&amp;藍都唔會做得大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似光時咁樣成個速遞協會杯鳩你已經收皮<br />\n仲未計佢日日搵人搞你鋪頭/員工已經令你做唔到生意<br />\n仲可以作啲罪名郁你户口，罰你錢<br />\n律政師一樣係幫兇，唔好諗住仲有法律"},{"pid":"93ca4351a83e1b573f7af980b6266706c68cd5a2","tid":1685050,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c1c11fa5d76fd95daad8f7b4bcd8f93c9675bd8","tid":1685050,"uid":244451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"715cf8e2285480cce2301fd