 class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:32:46.000Z","msg":"可以的話叫參與商戶收美金，架空港元"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:56:13.000Z","msg":"呢個好難<br />\n同埋會好唔方便<br />\n同路人夾硬用美金都有啲機會<br />\n但藍絲一定唔會咁做<br />\n我哋建立呢個圈唔係自己同自己玩<br />\n要賺埋藍絲錢再用返落黃圈入面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:24:00.000Z","msg":"開始就手足一齊用，慢慢就可以同化其他人"},{"pid":"6c2c2f85f7c3a99dd791b558bf6efe3f5b1d110d","tid":1685050,"uid":166528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T01:15:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"061f3f0dfa3d5f6efa6a3c26f6975216c3ca6af2","tid":1685050,"uid":135740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:31:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">想發達不妨睇一睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 整食評app(包含地圖)<br />\n2. 為呢個app成立公司 (IT部)(市場部)(財務部)(人事部) <br />\n3. 連結米豬連: 食評加黃店認證<br />\n4. 如果要取代openrice,我認為要:<br />\n- 整捐錢系統<br />\n- app內廣告收益 <br />\n- year pass計劃,去指定店鋪有95折優惠  <br />\n[除咗廣告,捐錢, year pass應該都係幾好既choice]<br />\n<br />\n最理想係黃金經濟圈可以cover哂衣同食先:<br />\n日用品 (光時)<br />\n食嘢 (呢個app既公司) 希望有啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">懶人包<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所有黃藍地圖暫時係非牟利,好打極有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有錢想創業既巴打不妨夾錢+聯絡米豬連團隊 食評認證雙管齊下<br />\n夾手夾腳做大個餅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">發到圍既機會幾大 想發達趁今鋪 有人做咗先個機會就冇嫁喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"365700d7f19f4338dab2f4b91b51c34d592c2635","tid":1685050,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:55:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be9fa2ca93342422056f5d9a5381f